name_blz.zh_TW: 物品:德魯伊T14守護者4P獎勵

description_blz.en_US: Increases the healing received from your Frenzied Regeneration by 10% and increases the dodge granted by your Savage Defense by an additional 5%.

description_blz.de_DE: Erhöht die Heilwirkung Eures Zaubers 'Rasende Regeneration' um 10% und den Ausweichbonus Eurer Fähigkeit 'Wilde Verteidigung' zusätzlich um 5%.

description_blz.ko_KR: 광포한 재생력의 치유량이 10%만큼 증가하고, 야생의 방어로 증가하는 회피율이 추가로 5%만큼 증가합니다.
